DON’T JUST WISH FOR IT – WORK FOR IT!
If you have been scrolling through Instagram or FB and found yourself saying – I want her butt – I want her stomach – I want her LIFE. .
STOP IT RIGHT NOW! .
Firstly focus on all the amazing qualities YOU have, then if what they have has highlighted something that YOU want, make a plan to make it happen and go out there and WORK FOR IT! .
You can have, be and do anything you want in this lifetime, all you have to do is believe in yourself because I know I believe in YOU!
.
Also remember that majority of people post their highlights reel, their best angle, best lighting photo , flawless light or airbrushed image so when your comparing remember all of that. It's a big reason why I share my tough times and don't edit my photos as I always want to keep it real so we can all try to support and relate to each other and know we can all achieve anything we want but we ALL have to choose our hard's and WORK hard!!!! I'm up at 4 am today to smash my emails and messages out so I have enough time in the day - what are you doing extra today to help dreams turn into reality?
.
